skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: thunderbird dining
des: Let Thunderbird Dining know what meal you would like to eat and if you have any dietary restrictions such as vegan or vegetarian. Thunderbird Dining will tell you all of your options for that meal at Southern Utah University's dining hall.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
